  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>Great ideas come to you naturally, often when your life depends on it.</p><p> You always have a plan, or at least parts of it.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• Increase the Intelligence ability score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• You can use your Intelligence modifier instead of your Dexterity modifier when making Initiative checks.</p><p>• When you would make a Dexterity saving throw, you can instead make an Intelligence saving throw.</p><p> You can use this effect twice per long rest.</p><p></p>",
